result.name: 2005-the-marine-conservation-society-seasearch-various-locations-in-dorset-diver-observations-a2
result.notes:
Seasearch dives undertaken in Dorset during 2005 - mostly dives organised by Dorset Wildlife Trust.  All survey records from individual dives, Seasearch weekends and specific studies are all included. In many cases, records are compiled from more than one form where divers were in close proximity to each other and covered the same habitats.
     Photographs taken on Dorset Wildlife Trust charter weekends are held by DWT in Dorchester.
